{"tid":1032963,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"又一城廁所個自動沖廁真係好垃圾（附解決方法）","createTime":"2019-02-22T18:20:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T00:39:17.000Z","uid":4154,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dd8cdb1a203dd5466c4a0adabeed3f627ceceead","tid":1032963,"uid":4154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T18:20:10.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母每次入去未屙已經幫你沖幾次水<br />\n特別係鋪好廁紙陣喺廁板<br />\n一轉身諗住除褲又同你沖一次<br />\n啲水彈到啲廁紙都係<br />\n搞到又要鋪過<br />\n屙緊嗰陣重衰<br />\n烏一烏低身又沖<br />\n反應慢啲彈唔切起身就成個屎忽都係<br />\n所以我諗咗用呢個方法<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gBimQZd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgBimQZd.png&h=d752b8b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用兩行廁紙（因為左右兩個sensor）<br />\n加啲廁板消毒酒精喺頂位等佢定住<br />\n遮撚住兩個濕鳩sensor<br />\n雖然係嘥啲紙<br />\n但總好過又嘥水又搞到自己屙得唔自在"},{"pid":"68b5d02cba591947052214030728d8941b43d513","tid":1032963,"uid":139873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T18:32:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b01a85147e5fcdab74984f3a1ccd1959cc6822e","tid":1032963,"uid":138740,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T18:38:14.000Z","msg":"最驚係痾痾下幫你沖水<br />\n成個屎忽彈到濕晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"608a73e47a13983dd07bef291a0247e60c98baab","tid":1032963,"uid":4154,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7b01a85147e5fcdab74984f3a1ccd1959cc6822e","tid":1032963,"uid":138740,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T18:38:14.000Z","msg":"最驚係痾痾下幫你沖水<br />\n成個屎忽彈到濕晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T18:54:06.000Z","msg":"係 郁一郁個身都沖水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a8266d58f8983f7792584fb39cbf207be29b9d7","tid":1032963,"uid":234317,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T23:24:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed7740096f263b27bd11d2934647616883843ad8","tid":1032963,"uid":80107,"